{"tid":1233432,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"龍和道，該佔/不該佔","createTime":"2019-06-16T18:47:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T19:00:23.000Z","uid":180285,"like":4,"dislike":37,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"148f2bc146a18449588f1f51974822ed36b6b90b","tid":1233432,"uid":180285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:47:29.000Z","msg":"利申，唔知對方係人定係鬼。<br />\n大家都唔會想見到今日成果被消耗。<br />\n<br />\n有幾點要考慮<br />\n1. 兄弟爬山，各自努力。（該佔）<br />\n<br />\n2. 呢場仗變到民意戰，正如有位市民話如果唔撒回，願意每星期都上街。今日兩百萬人上街有大部分都係因為放假先出到。如果聽日返工受阻，必然消耗民意。 （不該佔）<br />\n<br />\n3.剛才追post見到有人錄緊搬水馬情況，懷疑將會比位人入。（不該佔）<br />\n<br />\n...仲有其他原因待大家補充...<br />\n<br />\n大家覺得<br />\n應該佔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不該佔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一次開post有錯請輕力屌。"},{"pid":"97b709d2cecea839dbd87cc33f8805349425c3b1","tid":1233432,"uid":143210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:48:29.000Z","msg":"而家係和理非嘅回合！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1233067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1233067</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唱歌嘅時候就係夜晚<br />\n<br />\n衝嘅時候就係日頭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n守住非暴力嘅晚上就得"},{"pid":"2512d9a61e7a815d102e073c031ab10ecad55688","tid":1233432,"uid":180285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:50:11.000Z","msg":"求下大家快啲走。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1233335\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1233335</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n有post認為搬水馬係鬼。"},{"pid":"46c29dafdd51731826fa3d077af4ba5e49e6390d","tid":1233432,"uid":13867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:51:43.000Z","msg":"認真 覺得佔係可以<br />\n勇派跟左你和理非一日 冇勇到<br />\n集會已完 同埋佔完 守 我覺得係可以<br />\n衝就真係不了 有保留"},{"pid":"3c2d8952e46576453c76b00df61106cc1b045754","tid":1233432,"uid":157522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T18:52:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;